column5: Anybody from midland or penetang area.
Yeah, a couple prominent board members, they should be declarin' themselves shortly.
Yep as far as I know there is Maureen (motv8r) & Wayne (Irishfield) who are the prominent board members.  Then there is me.  What would you like to know?  Tom.

Not sure how prominant I am, but I live just outside Penetang...what can I do for you?  If it's a question about fishing in the area, not much help from me sad to say, at least not until I manage to get my boat out there and find my way around  Maureen
I'm a little south of there, Elmvale. CX
i have a cottage near penetang, fish the area quite often!
my parents own a cottage between Port Mcnicoll and the Martyr Shrine , it's close to the lighthouse on shore. I fish there about 5-6 times a year.
Oh yeah!  Work and play in the Penetang!!!  Spike
I heard it was a nice area until they allowed some aviation type dude and his family to move in.

No real important questions, im in midland/penetang everday, use to live in midland now live on orr lake. I was just wondering how many people were from around here. There is a few decent spots i fish from shore, and there is probably more that i just havent found yet. I could show you some hot spots for gobies if interested
